channel.title: BjorkPanel (Private Server UserPanel)
channel.description: Ok, this is my latest project. It's a php/mySQL system for runescape servers. A user can login and look at high-scores. Admins can edit account information and such through this system. It's not yet finished, but when it is i will post it here along with the source.
